Package: seqFiltR
Type: Package
Title: Sequence filtering tool
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christopher Nobles, Ph.D.
Maintainer: Christopher Nobles <cnobles@pennmedicine.upenn.edu>
Description: Tool used for filtering sequence files in fasta or fastq format. 
    Filtering can be preformed by several different indexing or sequence based 
    methods.
